After conventional induction treatment with R-CHOP (Rituximab, cyclophosphamide, adriamycin, vincristine and prednisone) the patients are randomized to: A: Consolidation with one dose of 90Y Ibritumomab tiuxetan (Zevalin(R)) 0,4 mCi/Kg B: Maintenance with 375 mg/m2 of Rituximab every 8 weeks during 24 months